{"tid":2162659,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"王亭之學斗數的故事（下） - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-08-18T08:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T17:23:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e5b280501db37e7d9c0fe2d6333aa73eadde2424","tid":2162659,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T08:44:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200818/6RQQOTJLNRD73ISSN7BTSSQ3UM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200818%2F6RQQOTJLNRD73ISSN7BTSSQ3UM%2F&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkFzmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=728df5df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200818%2F6RQQOTJLNRD73ISSN7BTSSQ3UM%2F&h=5fe15637\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200818/6RQQOTJLNRD73ISSN7BTSSQ3UM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n王亭之學斗數的故事（下） - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1W1xL0u0xLcaP6eUwr5q6MHtlj4=/1191x1215/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TW3M37Y6DBERJKQ5RIZS6VZSUU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1W1xL0u0xLcaP6eUwr5q6MHtlj4%3D%2F1191x1215%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTW3M37Y6DBERJKQ5RIZS6VZSUU.png&h=9a73669c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n王亭之自稱在一九七二年，「因為颱風襲港，懸掛九號風球」，班機停航，由是留台拜劉惠蒼為師，成為所謂中州派嫡傳弟子，更揚言手上有欽天監秘笈孤本。這故事很多人信以為真，就像那個「毒果創報黑幕」故事一樣，但也有人質疑，如術數界的傲天行先生。<br />\n<br />\n傲天行求證的方法，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。當然王亭之可說：「事隔廿年，一時誤記年分，不足為奇。」好，我現在再戳穿你第二個謊言。<br />\n<br />\n王亭之說中州派祖師，相傳是白玉蟾和吳景鸞。這說法並無明文記載，信不信由你，「姑妄聽之」可也。不幸的是，王亭之為了加強真實感，居然寫道：「惠老說，他的師傅姓俞，為清代漢學家俞正燮的後人。俞氏家傳天文之學，故於清代即入欽天監做個小官。」Oh my God，我是俞正燮粉絲啊！劉惠蒼是否存在，不得而知，但俞正燮寫的東西，我都「不幸」看過，不妨fact-check。<br />\n<br />\n一、 儘管俞氏博極群書，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n二、「俞氏家傳天文之學」不符事實。。。。。。。。。，何來「家傳天文之學」？<br />\n<br />\n三、「俞正燮的後人入欽天監做個小官」也是子虛烏有。。。。。。。。。。，何來所謂俞氏後人？<br />\n<br />\n亭老，您以為世上無人查到俞正燮後人嗎？以上資料在互聯網也找不到，很驚喜吧？"},{"pid":"6cbb8516819c85c0776d0941b3f68ecf6ffea0ad","tid":2162659,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:40:06.000Z","msg":"唔好意思搭單問下，王亭之著有《鐵板神數奇談》，但好似後來卻全盤否定鐵板神數，咁係咩事？究竟鐵板神數等術數是否可信？"},{"pid":"998ff33550fcfa4be68d54680653fc1cd27d414b","tid":2162659,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:58:14.000Z","msg":"王亭之藍到黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47fbb804cb1d0fe8aa55822833f10cfaef5a8ce2","tid":2162659,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:21:39.000Z","msg":"王亭之唔通臨老變老千 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e11b556a608e1299d51e18dc08bee4ecb0c6f10","tid":2162659,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cbb8516819c85c0776d0941b3f68ecf6ffea0ad","tid":2162659,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:40:06.000Z","msg":"唔好意思搭單問下，王亭之著有《鐵板神數奇談》，但好似後來卻全盤否定鐵板神數，咁係咩事？究竟鐵板神數等術數是否可信？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:32:29.000Z","msg":"鐵板神數出處有問題 , 由清代期間突然冒出 , 聲稱由宋代起源但就無任何較正式嘅歷史記錄<br />\n<br />\n而紫微斗數情況都差唔多 , 不過紫微斗數比較形象化 , 有圖睇 ,  所以較受坊間接受"},{"pid":"3da8811f949716b75e972d71955419825f89c8be","tid":2162659,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:33:36.000Z","msg":"XO醬係唔係佢發明?"},{"pid":"eb702738b544e9a909335860b722b03618e17435","tid":2162659,"uid":202577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cbb8516819c85c0776d0941b3f68ecf6ffea0ad","tid":2162659,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:40:06.000Z","msg":"唔好意思搭單問下，王亭之著有《鐵板神數奇談》，但好似後來卻全盤否定鐵板神數，咁係咩事？究竟鐵板神數等術數是否可信？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:32:51.000Z","msg":"有個親戚（算